# Discord LLM Bot Project Overview

This project implements a Discord bot that interfaces with various LLM backends (OpenAI-compatible APIs, KoboldCPP, Ollama) to provide AI chat capabilities in Discord servers.

## Core Features
- Direct interaction with users through mentions and replies
- Configurable LLM character profiles via character.json
- Support for multiple LLM backends
- Error handling with user-friendly messages

## Key Components
- [main.py](mdc:main.py) - Main bot entry point
- [config.py](mdc:config.py) - Configuration management
- [character.json](mdc:character.json) - LLM character configuration
- [requirements.txt](mdc:requirements.txt) - Project dependencies

## Configuration
The bot requires the following configuration:
1. Discord Bot Token
2. LLM API Key
3. LLM Server Address
4. Character Profile (character.json)

## Error Handling
